741
00:42:06,153 --> 00:42:09,233
♪Leaving only obsessions♪

742
00:42:10,553 --> 00:42:13,953
♪I've wandered in the world♪

743
00:42:14,453 --> 00:42:17,453
♪Yet cannot have it all♪

744
00:42:19,013 --> 00:42:22,283
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

745
00:42:22,603 --> 00:42:26,293
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

746
00:42:26,993 --> 00:42:28,923
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

747
00:42:29,463 --> 00:42:34,383
♪How could I ever forget♪

748
00:42:34,963 --> 00:42:37,243
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

749
00:42:37,243 --> 00:42:39,763
♪To spend time with you♪

750
00:42:40,013 --> 00:42:41,373
♪When we grow old♪

751
