♪Nothing will change♪

752
00:42:43,963 --> 00:42:45,563
♪The misty rains never cease♪

753
00:42:45,563 --> 00:42:48,423
♪Falling gently on your brow♪

754
00:42:48,423 --> 00:42:52,413
♪Lingering in my heart♪

755
00:42:52,413 --> 00:42:54,113
♪I would sever fate's ties♪

756
00:42:54,113 --> 00:42:56,533
♪To protect your smiling eyes♪

757
00:42:56,923 --> 00:43:00,793
♪Even if behind me lies a storm♪

758
00:43:00,793 --> 00:43:01,903
♪No matter the trials♪

759
